            , JUN. I am in partnership with my father, 
               <persName id="t18221023-17-person241">
                  Daniel 
                  Deacon
               <interp inst="t18221023-17-person241" type="surname" value="Deacon"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18221023-17-person241" type="given" value="Daniel"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18221023-17-person241" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
